"      </a>",
"      <br/>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_basics\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?20/3/20530?source=see_link\">",
"       Patient information: Travelers&rsquo; diarrhea (The Basics)",
"      </a>",
"     </p>",
"     <p>",
"      <a class=\"medical medical_patient\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?35/29/36308?source=see_link\">",
